    Algorithm

Step1:Start 

Step2:Read the limit 'n'

Step3:Read a Sortted array of 'n' element 

Step4:Read searchkey

Step5:Initialze left=0 ,right=n-1

Step6:Repeat the following step until left<=right  ( else goto step 7)

    Step6.1:mid=(left+right)/2   =>(if true goto Step6.2.1
                                      else got to Step6.3

    Step6.2:Check if key==a[mid]

        Step6.2.1:print element found at mid+1 th position

        Step6.2.2:goto step8

    Step6.3:Check if key <a[mid] =>if true goto step6.3.1
                                      else goto step6.4

        Step6.3:Check if key<a[mid]  =>if true goto step6.4

    Step6.4:Check if key>a[mid]  =>if true goto step 6.4.1

        Step6.4.1:left=mid-1

Step7:Check if(left<right)  =>if true goto step7.1
                                else goto step8
      Step7.1:Print"Element is not found"
      Step7.2:goto step8

Step8:Stop

